            "message": "=Hi there,\n\nYour AI-generated product description for \"{{ $json.productName }}\" is ready!\n\n📝 Title: {{ $json.english.title }}\n\n📋 Meta Description:\n{{ $json.english.metaDescription }}\n\n📄 Full Description:\n{{ $json.english.fullDescription }}\n\n🔑 SEO Keywords: {{ $json.english.seoKeywords }}\n\n✅ Bullet Points:\n{{ $json.english.bulletPoints ? $json.english.bulletPoints.join('\\n• ') : 'N/A' }}\n\nThis copy has been saved to your Product Descriptions spreadsheet.\n\nBest,\nYour Product Copy AI",
            "options": {},
